  "description": "Adds a few more weapons to Minecraft!",
  "body": "<center>\n  <h2>⚔️About⚔️</h2>\n</center>\n\nA Few More Weapons (AFMW) adds what it says: A few more weapons... and bit more. \n\nIt is a combat oriented mod aimed at improving/spicing up the vanilla combat (cuz crit spamming with pots is boring). Each weapon added fills a unique role and has specific use cases making pvp more strategic. \n\nCheck out the [GitHub wiki](https://github.com/Midget807/A-Few-More-Weapons/wiki) to see all the new features this mod adds!\n\n\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ad4d976c-e40d-439e-841f-dea3010c6f5d\", alt=\"overview image\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center>\n  <h2>Dependencies</h2>\n  <p>\n    See the specific AFMW versions for the dependency requirements and details. <br>\n    You can download specific dependencies when viewing the respective versions.\n  </p>\n  <span>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api/versions\", target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/81d40a60-1360-41e5-95bc-ff70ed12779c\", alt=\"Fabric Api Version\", width=150, height=50>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cardinal-components-api/versions\", target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e56dccc4-6072-4067-8119-eb387f8cabfe\", alt=\"CCA Version\", width=266, height=50>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/JamiesWhiteShirt/reach-entity-attributes.git\", target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/213b99f5-8012-4102-9e22-667d6b5e5bdd\", alt=\"REA Github\", width=248, height=50>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n</center>\n<center>\n  <span>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/emi/versions\", target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/739b13e4-2c4f-4033-92f5-5ddfa8f66766\", alt=\"EMI Version\", width=150, height=50>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n</center>\n\n\n",
